+# Modular Architecture Documentation
+
+## Overview
+
+This project has been restructured into a modular architecture to improve maintainability, scalability, and separation of concerns. The codebase is now organized into distinct modules based on functionality.
+
+## Python Modules
+
+### chromadb/core/
+Contains core business logic and entities that are used throughout the system.
+
+### chromadb/api/
+Contains API interfaces and implementations for different API layers.
+
+### chromadb/db/
+Database interfaces and implementations for various storage backends.
+
+### chromadb/server/
+Server components including HTTP server implementations.
+
+### chromadb/cli/
+Command-line interface components for the Chroma CLI.
+
+### chromadb/client/
+Client-side code for connecting to the Chroma server.
+
+### chromadb/segment/
+Segment management components for handling data segmentation.
+
+### chromadb/utils/
+General utility functions used across the system.
+
+### chromadb/config/
+Configuration management system.
+
+### chromadb/telemetry/
+Telemetry and monitoring components.
+
+### chromadb/auth/
+Authentication and authorization components.
+
+## Rust Modules
+
+### rust/worker/src/core/
+Core business logic and entities for the Rust worker.
+
+### rust/worker/src/database/
+Database interfaces and implementations for the Rust worker.
+
+### rust/worker/src/segment/
+Segment management for the Rust worker.
+
+### rust/worker/src/server/
+HTTP server components for the Rust worker.
+
+### rust/worker/src/config/
+Configuration management for the Rust worker.
+
+### rust/worker/src/utils/
+General utility functions for the Rust worker.
+
+## Go Modules
+
+### go/pkg/core/
+Core business logic and entities for the Go components.
+
+### go/pkg/database/
+Database interfaces and implementations for the Go components.
+
+### go/pkg/segment/
+Segment management for the Go components.
+
+### go/pkg/server/
+HTTP server components for the Go components.
+
+### go/pkg/config/
+Configuration management for the Go components.
+
+### go/pkg/client/
+Client-side code for connecting to the Go server components.
+
+### go/pkg/utils/
+General utility functions for the Go components.
\ No newline at end of file
